00:37:51.500 --> 00:37:53.570
are driving you toward it.

00:37:53.570 --> 00:37:55.070
You're aware of
what you're doing,

00:37:55.070 --> 00:37:56.450
but you really
want the chocolate

00:37:56.450 --> 00:37:57.980
and feel like you should eat it.

00:37:57.980 --> 00:38:00.170
CHRIS: Well, it tastes
good, and I get a lift.

00:38:02.462 --> 00:38:03.170
SEAN YOUNG: Good.

