So that's an example of,
if it's further away,

00:40:32.290 --> 00:40:34.720
then it's going to
be harder to do,

00:40:34.720 --> 00:40:36.520
it's not going to be
as easy, and you'll

00:40:36.520 --> 00:40:37.990
be less likely to do it.

00:40:37.990 --> 00:40:41.050
And how has that
worked out for you?

00:40:41.050 --> 00:40:42.970
CHRIS: It's lessened the intake.

